          <title>
            <string language="en">Voyager: Inspiring Generations</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Voyager: Anspornende Erzeugungen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Voyager : Générations Inspirantes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Voyager: Gerações Inspirando</string>

            <string language="x-mt-es">Voyager: Generaciones Inspirantes</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">For 30 years, Voyager has been broadening our view of the solar system and inspiring new generations to explore. For more information see: http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyager/voyager20070820/</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Für 30 Jahre hat Voyager unsere Ansicht des 
Solarsystems und der anspornenden neuen Erzeugungen erweitert, um zu 
erforschen. Zu mehr Information sehen Sie: 
http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyager/voyager20070820/</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Pendant 30 années, Voyager avait élargi 
notre avis sur le système solaire et les nouvelles générations 
inspirantes pour l'explorer. Pour plus d'information voyez : 
http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyageur/voyager20070820/</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Por 30 anos, Voyager broadening nossa opinião o 
sistema solar e as gerações novas inspirando para explorar. 
Para mais informação veja: 
http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyager/voyager20070820/</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Per 30 anni, Voyager sta estendendo nostro parere 
sul sistema solare e sulle generazioni nuove d'ispirazione per 
esplorare. Per le più informazioni veda: 
http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyager/voyager20070820/</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Για 30 έτη, ο ταξιδιώτης έχει διευρύνει την όψη 
μας του ηλιακού συστήματος και έχει εμπνεύσει τις νέες γενεές 
που εξερευνούν. Για περισσότερες πληροφορίες 
δείτε: http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyager/voyager20070820/</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Por 30 años, Voyager ha estado ensanchando 
nuestra opinión la Sistema Solar y las nuevas generaciones 
inspirantes para explorar. Para más información vea: 
http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/videos/voyager/voyager20070820/</string>
